  1445	### C16 — effects observe committed state only
  1446	
  1447	```
  1448	1 | default D applied-not-committed: a.set(1) | receipt; K0 a=1
  1449	2 | unrelated retirement flushes useSignalEffects | effect e evaluates committed-for-root: D not retired/locked ⇒ a=0 ✓ excluded
