  1461	### C17 — optimistic rollback
  1462	
  1463	No truncation surface exists (closed by deletion — React batches never
  1464	truncate; D2 folds committed=false batches). A public-API snapshot test
  1465	forbids accidental export of any truncation affordance. Optimistic UI
